{
  "stem": "1400.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was very happy, under the circumstances.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because I hoped that being close to the kitchen, I might be able to eat-- get some food.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But I was able to eat all the raw potato and raw cabbage I can muster down, because that's all we were cutting-- potato and cabbage, for months.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I was in Auschwitz four and a half months, which is-- very few people have been that long in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Because I got this job in the kitchen, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was in a work detail, and I went into a barrack where people who maintained the camp.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "In the meanwhile, people were shipped out to different parts of Germany to man the factories during the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Because the German people-- were-- were in the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And so they were no-- Jews were manning the factories and doing the production.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] transports were coming in, new transport, and going out transports.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I recall, there were machine gun guards on the outskirts of the railroad tracks, further away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's Jewish [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] prisoners who were ordering us around and pushing us around.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were ordered to do-- separate the capable people, the children, and the women, and the oldsters, different groups.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were doing their job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not to me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just don't recall.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if they were talking, they probably were talking in a different language.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They could've been Poles or Czech or Russian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But different-- from different countries.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because whoever arrived first, they get these jobs, which was good in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they were a job group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They called it the Kanadians, which were taking apart the packages, and find all the food and the goodies.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
